
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Scapular fracture' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And '14A: Process' radio button is enabled
And '14B: Body' radio button is enabled
And '14F: Glenoid fossa' radio button is enabled
And '14: Not further specified' radio button is enabled


When I select '14A: Process' radio button
Then '14A.1' radio button is enabled
And '14A.2' radio button is enabled
And '14A.3' radio button is enabled

When I select '14B: Body' radio button
Then '14B1' radio button is enabled
And '14B2' radio button is enabled

When I select '14F: Glenoid fossa' radio button
Then '14F0' radio button is enabled
And '14F1' radio button is enabled
And '14F2' radio button is enabled

When I select '14: Not further specified' radio button
Then 'Fracture older, consolidated' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspected' radio button is enabled
